For the first build steps, use:

```text
docs/implementation/FIRST_5_CODEX_PROMPTS.md
```

This file contains controlled prompts for:
1. read and summarize docs
2. scaffold app
3. add database migrations
4. add benchmark source types/validator
5. add engine core tests and progress-only analysis

Use these prompts in order.

